    <div class="container-fluid food-display-table">
        <div class="table-content">
            <h3>Hello!!</h3>
            <h4> Thank you for sigining up into the website of our restaurant. I hope we can help you to enjoy the food of our restaurant from home or your work place</h4>
            <h4>Here are some of the steps that needs to be followed while ordering food</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>First after logging into our website, the customer is taken to the categories of food item page.</li>
                <li>The customer can click on the photo of their desired category or the link and the food items present in that category is displayed</li>
                <li>The customer can click on the photo or click on "Add To Cart"link of the desired food item or can click on the read more if you want to look at the in</li>
                <li>A page will appear where the photo, name, rate(per piece/plate)is displayed and the quantity which has to be filled</li>
                <li>After filling on the quantity and clicking of "Add To Cart", the customer will be taken to the category page where can again order food items in the similar process</li>
                <li>After adding all the food items, the customer needs to click on the cart link at the top where list of all the food items added currently is displayed.</li>
                <li>After scrilling down, the customer needs to add the delivery address and the delivery detail.</li>
                <li>After that the customer is taken to the confirm page which when clicked on the confirm button will add the order in the admins page.</li>
                <li>If you have any problem regarding the food or delivery service, then you can click on the feedback link at the top of the screen</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
